{"tid":2517403,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"中國「長征五號」火箭失控    專家預測：恐墜人口密集區域","createTime":"2021-05-05T09:47:43.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-05T10:30:16.000Z","uid":255650,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"2e9bcb902e6685ae950b579973b85adf9064732a","tid":2517403,"uid":255650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T09:47:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2021/05/05/rovcketcrash/life-tech/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2021%2F05%2F05%2Frovcketcrash%2Flife-tech%2F&d=d89kjzbMxLru5B8Znw6mn4eonPPUtn1HApnj2AcFxYA%3D&h=c692fb93\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2021/05/05/rovcketcrash/life-tech/</a><br />\n中國於 4 月 29 日升空的中國長征五號 B 遙二運載火箭中，一截重達 21 噸的核心火箭段出現滾動，並正失控墜落中。據各國專家公佈的預測路徑，失控的火箭段還未能準確確認墜落的地點。<br />\n<br />\n長征五號 B 自上周四成功發射「天和號核心艙」後，其火箭卻與本體分離並高速翻滾和失控。 此舉引起了美國軍方的注意，當局也正運用雷達來追蹤這個核心火箭段，並把其命名為「2021-035B」。目前該核心火箭段以時速 2.8 萬公里的速度，在距海平面 160 至 170 公里高度繞行。據專家分析，目前仍無法預測「2021-035B」的準確墜落時間和位置，只能通過對運行軌道作出的分析，預計這些火箭碎片的墜落範圍大約為：北至北京、紐約、馬德里，南至智利、紐西蘭威靈頓，掉落範圍涵蓋了海洋甚至是人口稠密的住宅區。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/planet4589/status/1389055877349527556\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fplanet4589%2Fstatus%2F1389055877349527556&d=d89kjzbMxLru5B8Znw6mn4eonPPUtn1HApnj2AcFxYA%3D&h=e9e4ceb9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fplanet4589%2Fstatus%2F1389055877349527556&h=3993a046\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/planet4589/status/1389055877349527556</a><br />\n<br />\n對此，美國空軍第 18 太空控制中隊正在持續追蹤「2021-035B」的動向。<br />\n<br />\n資料來源: SpaceNews<br />\n<a href=\"https://spacenews.com/huge-rocket-looks-set-for-uncontrolled-reentry-following-chinese-space-station-launch/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fspacenews.com%2Fhuge-rocket-looks-set-for-uncontrolled-reentry-following-chinese-space-station-launch%2F&d=d89kjzbMxLru5B8Znw6mn4eonPPUtn1HApnj2AcFxYA%3D&h=21e90988\" target=\"_blank\">https://spacenews.com/huge-rocket-looks-set-for-uncontrolled-reentry-following-chinese-space-station-launch/</a>"},{"pid":"b0d335b135ccdee97a3349c7b56c2dfddf9a234e","tid":2517403,"uid":33263,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T09:48:44.000Z","msg":"愛國者飛彈要發射了"},{"pid":"9de39f101229c5d711a3394ff77f2f3d128e3b3d","tid":2517403,"uid":180233,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T09:49:34.000Z","msg":"中國點火？"},{"pid":"f8c67371d65b303328f57654d5d5b94a4612fb78","tid":2517403,"uid":58552,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T09:49:35.000Z","msg":"呢d次次事前聲大大<br />\n事後無影<br />\n廢事拍定手先"},{"pid":"0316e5bf8bc72b160a741fdd8912d9c1504ffd60","tid":2517403,"uid":228955,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T09:51:49.000Z","msg":"上海pls"},{"pid":"1d1269b81c78452b6986e10a848e2cf9a9079004","tid":2517403,"uid":97078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T09:53:19.000Z","msg":"如果中紐約算唔算開戰"},{"pid":"c36b5c4e4225a35ff49805cacc2949fb3a694154","tid":2517403,"uid":347925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T09:54:31.000Z","msg":"預計幾時到達地面?"},{"pid":"2396d906a04606c80a575cff416f188ef8e866c4","tid":2517403,"uid":45660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T09:54:45.000Z","msg":"愈大劑愈好<br />\n加速<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cd179ec1352f57fe92db46ce4d2a2de08294ea3","tid":2517403,"uid":311835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T09:55:09.000Z","msg":"基連 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9527035cfdcd26ae0c6d49d1e3813ce9c2543b45","tid":2517403,"uid":120935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T09:55:33.000Z","msg":"星塵作戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84eb04ea5e1dc8ee7da908422cc06856a248490f","tid":2517403,"uid":393300,"lik